        },
        {
          "heading": "样例说明",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "heading": "样例解释 1",
              "level": 3,
              "blocks": [
                {
                  "type": "p",
                  "html": "$126$ 是 $21$ 的倍数，且满足 $6 \\geq 2 \\geq 1 \\geq 0 \\geq \\ldots$，所以它是一个好数。不存在比 $126$ 更小的且是 $21$ 倍数的好数，因此输出 $126$。",
                  "depth": 1
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "heading": "样例解释 4",
              "level": 3,
              "blocks": [
                {
                  "type": "p",
                  "html": "答案可能是 $2^{64}$ 或更大。",
                  "depth": 1
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "题解",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "把<strong>余数和个位数作为状态</strong>，发现<strong>最多只有</strong> $10N$ <strong>个状态</strong>，直接跑 $BFS$ 就搞完所有状态就行了。本题答案可能较长，所以用<strong>回溯法</strong>处理。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "heading": "状态定义",
          "level": 4,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "我们需要在搜索过程中记录什么信息？",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>当前的余数</strong>：我们要找 $X \\% N == 0$，所以必须记录当前拼凑出的数字模 $N$ 的余数 $r$。",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>末位数字</strong>：为了保持“好数”的性质（数字递增），我们需要知道当前数字的最后一位 $d$，这样下一位只能填 $\\ge d$ 的数字。",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "因此，定义状态为 <code>(last_digit, yu)</code>，表示当前数字模 $N$ 余数为 <code>yu</code>，且最后一位是 <code>last_digit</code>。",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "状态转移",
          "level": 4,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "假设当前状态是 <code>(now, yu)</code>，我们可以追加一个新的数字 <code>to</code>（满足 $d \\le to \\le 9$）：",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "新的数值：$NewVal= OldVal \\times 10 + to$",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "新的余数：$nyu = (yu \\times 10 + to) \\% N$",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "新的状态：<code>(to, nyu)</code>",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "代码",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "struct node {\n\tint now, yu;\n};\nstruct node2 {\n\tint st, pnow, pyu;\n};\nnode2 pre[10][N];\nvoid solve(int CASE)\n{\n\tint n; cin >> n;\n\tvar Q = queue<node>();\n\tfa(i, 1, 9) {\n\t\tint yu = i % n;\n\t\tpre[i][yu] = { -1, -1, -1 };\n\t\tQ.push({ i, yu });\n\t}\n\t\n\twhile (Q.size()) {\n\t\tvar[now, yu] = Q.front();\n\t\tQ.pop();\n\n\t\tif (yu == 0) {\n\t\t\tstring ans;\n\t\t\tans.pb(now + '0');\n\t\t\twhile (pre[now][yu].st != -1) {\n\t\t\t\tconst var& [st, pnow, pyu] = pre[now][yu];\n\t\t\t\tans.pb(pnow + '0');\n\t\t\t\tnow = pnow, yu = pyu;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\treverse(all(ans));\n\t\t\tcout << ans << endl;\n\t\t\treturn;\n\t\t}\n\t\tfa(i, now, 9) {\n\t\t\tint nyu = (yu * 10 + i) % n;\n\t\t\tif (!pre[i][nyu].st) {\n\t\t\t\tpre[i][nyu] = { 1, now, yu };\n\t\t\t\tQ.push({ i,nyu });\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\tcout << -1 << endl;\n\treturn;\n}",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
